---
title: Vietnamese-Style Pulled Pork Bowl with Pickled Onion & Garlic Rice
description: Discover classic Vietnamese flavours with a whole new twist! Take tasty garlic rice piled with saucy pulled pork and sautéed garlic veggies, and you’ve got a dinner-time hit. Serve with quick-pickled onion for an extra punch of flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ftc-nz-bun-cha-pulled-pork-bowl-012e45ee.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/ftc-nz-bun-cha-pulled-pork-bowl-5f6bfdc03ed643583447ef34-745d3dcc.pdf
